Use cases:

Customer

-subscribe to bakery
-place an order/modify order
-add breads
-add quantity
-lookup offered breads
-modify personal and contact information
-make payment
-change payment method
-check order status


Bakery
-lookup customer information
-adding to /modifying to the list of breads offered
-modifying price of breads and delivery
-taking payment
-notifying customer about status of delivery
-answering customers' questions
-adding/updating recipe
-adding/updating ingredients
-maintaining inventory
-maintaining list of breads to cook for the day
-maintaining customers' history of orders
-maintaining list of orders for the week
-maintaining list of ingredients to order for the next week 